import React, {
  Fragment,
  Component
} from 'react';
import {
  Helmet
} from 'react-helmet';
/* import './styles/styles.scss'; */

class Register extends Component {
  render() {
    return ( <
      Fragment >
      <
      Helmet > < title > Nimelssa Quiz - Registeration page < /title></Helmet > * / <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      form className = "col s12" >
      <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s6" >
      <
      input placeholder = "Enter Full Name"
      id = "full_name"
      type = "text"
      className = "validate" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "first_name" > First Name < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s6" >
      <
      input placeholder = "Enter Matric"
      id = "matric_number"
      type = "number"
      className = "validate" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "matric_number" > Matric Number < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      div className = 'row' >
      <
      div className = "input-field col s6" >
      <
      input placeholder = "Enter Matric"
      id = "matric_number"
      type = "number"
      className = "validate" > < /input> <
      label
      for = "matric_number" > Matric Number < /label> <
      /div> <
      /div> <
      /form> <
      /div> <
      /Fragment>
    )
  }
}
export default Register;
